parameters:
\n< Serena >I can't read a book in peace dressed
like this...

\n< Lady >It seems that slimes inhabit the area
near the spirit herbs. Please be
careful, okay?

I'm back. Here's the herb I've procured.
Please confirm it.\n< Serena >

Oh, you've returned quite quickly. As
expected of someone I've taken under my
wing. You're very capable.\n< Woman >

Just a moment, please. Let's see, the
compendium... umm...\n< Woman >

I have a question, what exactly is this
herb?\n< Serena >
...What do you mean?\n< Woman >

Nothing in particular. I was just
curious.\n< Serena >

...This herb grows by sipping on the
blood of the living.\n< Woman >

Deep in the forest shrouded in darkness
and miasma... when frost descends and
fog arises, a demon comes to leave a
sacrifice.\n< Woman >

As the bed of grass envelops the
sacrifice, the body vanishes into the
earth, and by the next morning, a
splendid flower blooms...\n< Woman >
A creepy ecology indeed.\n< Serena >

Ohoho, it's just a tasteless legend. Ah,
this petal's base matches the
characteristics exactly.\n< Woman >

There's no mistake. Thank you, little
adventurer. With this, the request is
complete.\n< Woman >
Hmm. Then I'll sign here... Indeed.\n< Serena >

...But if that's the case, could it be
that the person I met deep in the forest
was that demon?\n< Serena >
Oh? Did you meet someone?\n< Woman >

Yes. A young woman. She had an air of
resignation about her.\n< Serena >

The woman was fervently plucking those
herbs. Yet she claimed they were
unnecessary. Fortunately, she gave them
to me.\n< Serena >
Oh my, well... that is... let's see...\n< Woman >

Surely, she must have been a woman as
sinful as a demon.\n< Woman >
...\n< Serena >

\V[2501]\n< Serena > left. Well, it doesn't matter. It's
pointless to ponder
'　何が何やらわからぬが、とにかく目的は達した。宿へ戻って今日は休もう。'

parameters: Is everything alright?\n< Serena >
\n< Woman >Eek!

Are you the one who put out the request
at the guild?\n< Serena >
\n< Woman >Huh? Oh... yes, that's right... but why?
I want to hear the details!\n< Serena >

Ah, are you an adventurer...? In that
case, please come in.\n< Woman >
I'll be intruding then!\n< Serena >
That's how it is.\n< Woman >
Sigh...\n< Serena >
What seems to be the matter?\n< Woman >

No... it's nothing... I just had my own
expectations... and they weren't met...\n< Serena >

To summarize the story... you're engaged
to a certain city nobleman.\n< Serena >

You've told him that you have no past
experience with men.\n< Serena >

But in reality, you do. You thought it
wouldn't be found out if you kept
silent.\n< Serena >

However, he brought out something called
the "Unicorn's Saddle"... a magic item
that determines past romantic
experiences.\n< Serena >

He wants you to ride it to prove that
you are truly a pure maiden...\n< Serena >

How rude! Just thinking about it makes
me so angry!\n< Woman >

At my age, it's impossible not to have
had a man! Think with some common sense!\n< Woman >

However, for an unmarried woman to
associate with a man is considered
adultery.\n< Serena >

It's a serious crime. I've heard that
depending on the case, one could be
beheaded or burned at the stake.\n< Serena >

Hohoho, that's just for show. No one
takes it seriously these days.\n< Woman >

That's right, except for this foolish
noble...!\n< Woman >

...But even so, I can't let such a good
marriage proposal slip away.\n< Woman >

So, to deceive the Unicorn's Saddle, you
need special panties woven with a
spiritual herb...\n< Serena >

Yes, it was very difficult to find
out... but this is where money and time
should be spent!\n< Woman >

If it can change my life for the next
several decades, I won't hesitate!\n< Woman >

So I just need to procure this spiritual
herb?\n< Serena >

Please do. The habitat of the spiritual
herb is deep in the forest. Follow the
butterflies that glow with a blue
phosphorescence.\n< Woman >

But that place is also a dangerous area
infested with monsters. It's much too
much for a frail woman like me...\n< Woman >

Deep in the forest, marked by blue
butterflies. Attracted by the nectar of
flowers... Understood. I'll go collect
it right away.\n< Serena >

Oh, are you leaving already? Would you
care to join me for tea first?\n< Woman >

I'll pass. It's a simple request. I want
to finish it today.\n< Serena >

It took quite some time just to hear out
the story.\n< Serena >

Oh dear, hahaha, my apologies. I got
carried away with our conversation.\n< Woman >

It's because your manners and behavior
are impeccable.\n< Woman >

Every single action, you understood its
meaning and responded accordingly. It
was so delightful... I got carried away.\n< Woman >

Where did you learn such things? Your
family must have been very passionate
about education.\n< Woman >

You also have such a dignified
appearance... It's a waste for you to be
an adventurer in such a rural town.\n< Woman >

Yes. When this request is completed...
and when my marriage is successfully
arranged...\n< Woman >

Yes. I will surely invite you to high
society events.\n< Woman >

With your qualities, you could certainly
serve as a noble's consort. If you play
your cards right, you might even aim for
the position of a legal wife, depending
on the household.\n< Woman >

Just a bit to the north, there's a
bachelor baron. He would be an excellent
target for you.\n< Woman >

I will surely introduce you to him.
Please do your best to succeed in this
request.\n< Woman >

...If I suggested to my father that I
wanted to marry a baron, he would
probably faint on the spot.\n< Serena >

Oh, I'm sorry. Your voice was so soft.
What did you say just now?\n< Woman >
It's nothing. I'll be going now.\n< Serena >

Now then... If it's this forest, it's
best to leave town from the south. Once
I'm prepared, I'll head out from the
south.\n< Serena >

\n< Erika >So that's where we'll start today.
